title: G-Trigger
description:
Setup triggers on which a reaction will happen.

Trigger options:
 - Key pressed
 - Packet send to server
 - Packet send to client
 - You say command
 - Anyone says command

Reaction options:
 - Send packet to server
 - Send packet to client

NOTE: Read the release notes page for a list of all functionalities

title: GChatSaver
description:
GChatSaver is an extension for saving all user chats and room information

Saves all user chats (whispers included)
Saves Room infos (room name, room owner, room description)
Saves chat logs in the Extension folder
You can easily access your chat log by typing :gchat
You can see all the filtering options by typing :gchatfilters which will show you a list on how to add, remove or clean filters.

title: Outfit Copy
description:
Copy everyone's outfit.

:copy x - Copy someone
:outfitcombine x y type - Combine outfits
(type: a number between 1-3 that defines the type of combination. If empty, 3 will be used.)
:outfitcycle - Cycle through the outfits of everyone in the room
:outfitstop - Stop the command above

title: Outfit Randomizer
description:
Randomize your outfit or copy the outfit from someone in the same room

:outfit [m/f/u] -> Get random outfit specified gender (optional)
:outfit copy [name] -> Copy outfit of user with specified name or last clicked if no name specified
